Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我們生活的這個層次  還有其他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We live on one level of existence, but there are others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,到處充滿了隱藏著的其他維度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These hidden dimensions of reality are everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,從許多光年以外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Far away, across the light years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到我們的腳下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beneath our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至在我們的體內\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even inside you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們由原子組成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are made of atoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們眼睛中的原子數量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are more atoms in your eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,比已知宇宙中所有星系的星星數量還多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than there are stars and all the galaxies of the known universe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,上述情況也適用於任何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same is true of any solid object
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,比你的指尖稍大的實體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}larger than the tip of your little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我由30萬億億億複雜排列的原子組成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a collection of three billion, billion, billion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是名叫尼爾·德葛拉司·泰森的原子組合體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}intricately arranged atoms called Neil Degrasse Tyson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也是一樣  只是名字不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are a similar collection with a different name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們通常不會這麼認為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't usually think of ourselves this way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這個級別的存在超過了我們感官的範疇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because that level of reality lies beyond the realm of our senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我們不會就此停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're not gonna let that stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還要繼續探究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can go deeper into the wonder.
